response: Fraser was the son of Mary Ursula Cynthia Gwendolen (Macdonnell) and Ian Fraser, Baron Fraser of Tullybelton, a prominent Scottish lawyer who later became a Law Lord. He was educated at Eton College and St John's College, Oxford where he read Philosophy, Politics and Economics.‘FRASER OF CORRIEGARTH’, Who's Who 2017, A & C Black, an imprint of Bloomsbury Publishing plc, 2017 After graduation, he worked at various jobs in the financial sector. His major jobs included:
| Ian Fraser, Baron Fraser of Tullybelton, Lord of Appeal in Ordinary 1975-1985
